      "title": "Rational G-matrices with rational eigenvalues",
      "abstract": "Abstract A study of the totally rational (entries and eigenvalues) centralizer of an Abelian group, G , is applied to the problem of determing which strongly regular graphs admit such a G as a egular automorphism group."
